  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Anthropometric data of infants' face will be obtained using special 3D scanners and software.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A digital camera will be used to take a 3D picture the face of each infant. Off line
      measurements of landmarks on the face will be marked and dimensions will be calculated using
      a special analysis software.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
